name: CROWN
description:
Loyalty and sincerity are the main capital in a service, a strong soul does not mean always ambitious to get what he wants, but a strong soul is a soul that is able to maintain and patiently accept everything that happens, loyalty and sincerity starts from love. and the fruit of love is patience, and that patience is the key to unlocking the wild soul.

FLY SERIES - WILD SOUL VOL.3
